00:24:53.950 --> 00:24:56.000
it describes how
many particles go

00:24:56.000 --> 00:24:58.400
through a space
in a certain time.

00:24:58.400 --> 00:25:02.400
And then there's the number
of particles that are there.

00:25:02.400 --> 00:25:06.740
If we're going with
