00:31:09.820 --> 00:31:12.170
have a different isotope.

00:31:12.170 --> 00:31:13.970
But oftentimes you won't have--

00:31:13.970 --> 00:31:17.180
the burning process won't
produce the same isotopes

00:31:17.180 --> 00:31:18.650
as the decay.

00:31:18.650 --> 00:31:21.320
So the situation we looked at
on Friday when we said let's

00:31:21.320 --> 00:31:22.590
