00:33:35.050 --> 00:33:37.750
or pull the rabbit out
of the reactor then

00:33:37.750 --> 00:33:40.390
the production and destruction
by neutrons is over

00:33:40.390 --> 00:33:42.460
but the decay keeps going.

00:33:42.460 --> 00:33:44.890
Which means if you wait
too long, like for some

00:33:44.890 --> 00:33:48.170
of those short isotopes, if
