00:36:53.190 --> 00:36:56.100
and you'll say n2 would
have to equal lambda

00:36:56.100 --> 00:37:00.940
1 over lambda 2 times n1.

00:37:00.940 --> 00:37:06.960
Which is n1 0 e to
the minus lambda 1 t.

00:37:06.960 --> 00:37:11.400
So if you want to find that
point right there in time,

00:37:11.400 --> 00:37:14.730
you can solve this.

